lead_paragraph: A judge has ordered a competency evaluation for a Phoenix woman accused of throwing a shoe at Hillary Clinton while the former U.S. secretary of state addressed a convention audience in Las Vegas.

headline.main: Exam Set for Accused Hillary Clinton Shoe-Thrower
